{
  "stem": "734.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said-- and my people were there with the wagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, why don't we open a window and I'll throw the bread out? you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll throw-- it will be easier than to come in and carry it up and down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, OK, you can do that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we opened the-- the-- the window.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would-- and he would stand by me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I would simply take the bread off the shelves, two loaves at a time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I would count.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One, two.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Each time, I threw out two breads.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my people would catch them and put them in the crate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was a very simple matter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he liked the idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he stood there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at some point, he got bored.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He would walk away to the other end of the barrack because some other people came in for something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I kept throwing bread without counting loud, you see?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this is how we had six or eight loaves more than we should have.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I thought, God, what am I going to do with eight loaves of bread extra?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They'll-- they'll shoot us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They'll kill us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We cannot simply eat them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We cannot take them with us to camp because it'll be visible.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You cannot take a loaf of bread and stuck-- and stick it in your pocket.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All-- so-- anyway, on the way back to the plant, I had this little area where the-- the bread had to be cut, distributed according to the list, to the department.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's say the sheet metal workers were getting 40 portions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The other were getting 22 portions, et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
